    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. Six factors appropriately scoped as not-assessed at MRL 2. Quantitative validation comparison demonstrates CFD predictions within \u00b115% of experimental NIH values with RH < 1 across all operating points. UQ campaign results discussed in validation report confirm robustness of conclusions to parameter variation. The credibility body of evidence is sufficient to support use of the CFD model for identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device. Decision: Accepted.",
